### Get player wallet balance
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wallet/player1

### Get crypto price
GET http://localhost:3000/api/prices/BTC

### Get game state
GET http://localhost:3000/api/game/state

### Place bet
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player1",
  "usdAmount": 10,
  "currency": "BTC"
}

### Cash out
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cashout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player1"
}

### Place ETH bet
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player2",
  "usdAmount": 25,
  "currency": "ETH"
}

### Check another player wallet
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wallet/player2